snippet.title: Philophobia: The Fear of Love - Itch.io Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist Philophobia: The Fear of Love on Steam here: http://bit.ly/2XLA52q

Philophobia is a game where love is literal Hell, and all of the enemies are hearts. Feb 10th, fight your way through 100+ heart-breaking scenarios, 6 realms of misery, and 5 stages of grief.
